                <h1>Pair of juniors chosen as 2017 Goldwater Scholars </h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/b7540901-a4e5-4dc1-852a-dcf3011a52cd.sized-1000x1000.png?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;John&#x20;Lu&#x20;and&#x20;Karen&#x20;Xu&#x20;are&#x20;two&#x20;out&#x20;of&#x20;240&#x20;students&#x20;who&#x20;will&#x20;receive&#x20;the&#x20;Goldwater&#x20;scholarship.&amp;nbsp&#x3B;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>John Lu and Karen Xu are two out of 240 students who will receive the Goldwater scholarship.&nbsp;</p>

                            
                        </div>
                    </figure>
                
                                    <div class="row  mt-4 mb-0 mb-md-4">
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                            <aside class="author-name">
                                    
    
                                    
            By <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/lexi-kadis">Lexi Kadis</a>
                                                             and                     <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/vir-patel">Vir Patel</a>
                                        
                                <div class="mt-1">
                                    <span class="can-localize">April 6, 2017 | 12:38am EDT</span>
                                </div>
                            </aside>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 text-left text-md-right d-print-none">
                            <ul class="social-links list-unsyled list-inline mt-4 mt-md-0">
                                <li class="list-inline-item"><a href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https://www.dukechronicle.com/article/2017/04/pair-of-juniors-chosen-as-2017-goldwater-scholars" target="_blank" class="sends-events" data-ga-category="Share" data-ga-action="click" data-ga-label="facebook" data-ga-value="CURL"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a></li>
